      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，P2和P1都要标注active状态，而且需要注明它们属于HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine模块。终止状态统一用done样式，P3和P4的完成时间点分别是14和15。",
      "elements_involved": [
